#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.inotify-survey.metainfo.xml:10
msgid "inotify Survey"
msgstr "inotify 調查"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.inotify-survey.metainfo.xml:11
msgid "Surveys inotify state of the system"
msgstr "調查系統的 inotify 狀態"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.inotify-survey.metainfo.xml:13
msgid ""
"Have you ever wondered why Dolphin or any other application stopped noticing "
"file changes? Chances are you ran out of inotify resources. kde-inotify-"
"survey to the rescue! Sporting a KDED module to tell you when things are "
"getting dicey and a CLI tool to inspect the state of affairs."
msgstr ""
"您是否曾經疑惑過為什麼 Dolphin 或其他任何應用程式沒辦法繼續發現檔案變更？這很"
"可能代表您用盡了 inotify 資源。kde-inotify-survey 會幫助您！它提供一個 KDED "
"模組來告訴您資源即將用盡，也有一個命令列工具讓您檢查 inotify 的狀態。"

#. (itstool) path: component/developer_name
#: org.kde.inotify-survey.metainfo.xml:16
msgid "Harald Sitter &lt;sitter@kde.org&gt;"
msgstr "Harald Sitter &lt;sitter@kde.org&gt;"
